    <item>
      <title>巴西旨在通过 Eletrobras 基金降低电费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/brazil-aims-to-lower-electricity-bills-with-eletrobras-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位熟悉该计划的官员透露，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦打算下周发布一项临时措施，旨在通过将该国最大发电公司所欠款项证券化来降低巴西电价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/brazil-aims-to-lower-electricity-bills-with-eletrobras-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯尼·桑德斯希望下周会见 Novo 首席执行官，讨论 Ozempic 价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/bernie-sanders-wants-to-meet-novo-ceo-next-week-on-ozempic-price</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伯尼·桑德斯 (Bernie Sanders) 希望下周与诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 高管会面，讨论降低其重磅药物 Ozempic 的价格，这引发了有关治疗糖尿病和肥胖症的 GLP-1 药物成本的争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/bernie-sanders-wants-to-meet-novo-ceo-next-week-on-ozempic-price</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:50:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在 X Post 上痛骂法官的女儿。法庭称这不是她</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/trump-bashed-judge-s-daughter-on-x-post-court-says-it-s-not-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据州法院系统发言人称，唐纳德·特朗普引用了一个虚假的社交媒体账户，虚假声称主持其刑事封口费审判的纽约法官的女儿发布了前总统入狱的照片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/trump-bashed-judge-s-daughter-on-x-post-court-says-it-s-not-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的二号人物安吉拉·雷纳在未来工党政府中寻求新的权力基础</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/starmer-deputy-angela-rayner-seeks-new-power-base-in-future-uk-labour-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔·斯塔默的副手安吉拉·雷纳计划在英国政府核心建立一个强大的新部门，以在反对党工党赢得下届大选时巩固她的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/starmer-deputy-angela-rayner-seeks-new-power-base-in-future-uk-labour-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使希望推动 Blackstone 和 KKR 对印度进行更多投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/us-envoy-wants-to-drive-more-blackstone-kkr-investment-to-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻印度大使表示，他希望增加美国养老基金和 KKR 等私募股权公司的投资。公司和黑石公司进入南亚经济，以利用其快速增长的优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/us-envoy-wants-to-drive-more-blackstone-kkr-investment-to-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯阻止联合国朝鲜核计划专家小组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/russia-blocks-extending-un-panel-on-north-korea-nuclear-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯否决了联合国安理会延长专家小组任期的决议，该专家小组已报告朝鲜核武库发展情况 15 年，突显莫斯科和平壤之间的关系日益密切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/russia-blocks-extending-un-panel-on-north-korea-nuclear-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
